d":208484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T06:48:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cM8LDQa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcM8LDQa.png&h=02707ef9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Aa1tBEB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAa1tBEB.jpg&h=fee8aedb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XaY0sMh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXaY0sMh.jpg&h=2a9c28ec&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T06:52:20.000Z","msg":"點解終點會又泳池又零炭天地？<br />\n姐係可以等人揀點行？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T07:33:51.000Z","msg":"終點係零碳 第一張poster唔記得改<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b05435835b05ec155cd3483526db9792ce58c281","tid":1490313,"uid":56223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T07:54:38.000Z","msg":"反送中運動持續，有市民發起本周六（24日）在觀塘舉行名為「燃點香港，全民覺醒」的遊行。遊行申請人今日與警方就遊行活動進行磋商，指由於警方多番對原定路線提出質疑，決定提出新路線，目前仍有待警方發出不反對通知書。<br />\n<br />\n遊行申請人劉頴匡表示，遊行原計劃在駿業街公園遊樂場起步，經觀塘道前往觀塘游泳池，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>惟警方擔心取道觀塘道會對交通造成影響。因此他提出改行海濱道，並以九龍灣零碳天地作為終點。</strong></span>預計遊行有四千人參與，確實路線有待警方發出不反對通知書落實。<br />\n<br />\n今次的觀塘遊行除了五大訴求之後，亦會關注智慧燈柱涉及的個人私隱及監控問題。政府推動多功能智慧燈柱試驗計劃為期三年，會在中環和金鐘、銅鑼灣和灣仔、尖沙咀、觀塘和啟德發展區，分階段安裝約 400 支智慧燈柱，其中九龍灣常悅道、啟德承啟道和觀塘市中心，已有 50 支在六月底投入服務，由於燈柱設有全景攝影機，市民憂慮燈柱會用於監控。<br />\n<br />\n此外原訂8月18日舉行的荃葵青遊行，由於讓路予民陣大遊行，早前宣布會延期一周至8月25日舉行。遊行亦正向警方申請不反對通知書。網上流傳的民宣指，遊行起步時間為當日三時半，將由葵涌運動場遊行至荃灣公園。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%A7%80%E5%A1%98-824-%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C-%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%E4%BA%BA%E6%9B%B4%E6%94%B9%E8%B7%AF%E7%B7%9A-%E5%B0%9A%E5%BE%85%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E6%89%B9%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E9%80%9A%E7%9F%A5%E6%9B%B8/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25A7%2580%25E5%25A1%2598-824-%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%25A1%258C-%25E7%2594%25B3%25E8%25AB%258B%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%259B%25B4%25E6%2594%25B9%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E7%25B7%259A-%25E5%25B0%259A%25E5%25BE%2585%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%2589%25B9%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%25B0%258D%25E9%2580%259A%25E7%259F%25A5%25E6%259B%25B8%2F&d=QZ1X7Ww%2BB3pe%2FYPW%2Fe6VufzvTpW%2BvScgizIMFshFG5Q%3D&h=306a1ff6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25A7%2580%25E5%25A1%2598-824-%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%25A1%258C-%25E7%2594%25B3%25E8%25AB%258B%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%259B%25B4%25E6%2594%25B9%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E7%25B7%259A-%25E5%25B0%259A%25E5%25BE%2585%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%2589%25B9%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%25B0%258D%25E9%2580%259A%25E7%259F%25A5%25E6%259B%25B8%2F&h=1314b2e8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%A7%80%E5%A1%98-824-%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C-%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%E4%BA%BA%E6%9B%B4%E6%94%B9%E8%B7%AF%E7%B7%9A-%E5%B0%9A%E5%BE%85%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E6%89%B9%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E9%80%9A%E7%9F%A5%E6%9B%B8/</a><br />\n<br />\n點觸要行無人既工廠區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n政府真係唔怕你行入面<br />\n如果行觀塘道，政府先會知驚"},{"pid":"b76e557e7749a9a6f1f27324af6dfe000bf7c4cc","tid":1490313,"uid":56223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T07:57:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fe2616d4d336c3312371f308ffd94652a2c0354","tid":1490313,"uid":56223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T08:06:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"810b3db12f7aafeba9abde319e00a7d34d276095","tid":1490313,"uid":56223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T08:17:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e51bfd3fb7ff8604cb3a7587d98d40045363b949","tid":1490313,"uid":56223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T08